text.section:
The department may:
Conduct hearings;
Administratively subpoena and examine under oath persons whose activities are subject to KRS 247.232 to 247.236;
Issue administrative subpoenas and examine the business records, books, and accounts of persons whose activities are subject to KRS 247.232 to 247.236; and
Request any other information necessary to assist the department in properly performing the department's duties.
